con:testCase.name: StopReactivate
con:testCase.con:description:
This testcase displays the flow of the PIN Action: STOP and REACTIVATE. Here an inernational payment is created. The then actions STOP and then REACTIVATE is performed on the payment.
Expected Flow: Payment Create (Future Value Date) -> RFDD -> STOP Action -> STOPPED -> REACTIVATE Action -> REACTIVATED -> RFDD -> RFPE -> CIPE.
